From 71ed773862716ff3a4def1884fa1d7f427f1ea47 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Gerald Combs <gerald@wireshark.org>
Date: Fri, 5 Oct 2012 18:52:42 +0000
Subject: [PATCH] Add a capture_file * element to packet_range_t and pass it
 explicitly in packet_range_init(). Get rid of global cfile references in
 packet-range.c. C++-ize packet-range.h. Shuffle some includes around.

svn path=/trunk/; revision=45333
---
 cfile.h                   |  2 ++
 file.c                    |  2 +-
 file.h                    |  4 +---
 fileset.h                 |  1 -
 packet-range.c            | 45 ++++++++++++++++++++++-----------------
